	bool "MTK_BMA222E_NEW for Mediatek package"
	default n
	help
	Say Y here if you have MTK_BMA222E_NEW touch panel BMA222_LOWPASS.

	If unsure, say N.

	To compile this dirver as a module, choose M here: the
	module will be called.

